com.flowpowered.commons.map.impl

Class TSyncIntObjectHashMap<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flowpowered.commons.map.impl.TSyncIntObjectHashMap<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    TSyncIntObjectMap<V>, gnu.trove.map.TIntObjectMap<V>

    public class TSyncIntObjectHashMap<V>
extends Object
implements TSyncIntObjectMap<V>
    This is a synchronised version of the Trove IntObjectHashMap. Read/write locks are used to synchronise access. By default, it creates 16 sub-maps and there is a separate read/write lock for each submap.
